### Branch Naming Rules
- Use lowercase with hyphens (kebab-case)
- Include ticket number when applicable: `feature/AUTH-123-user-login`
- Keep names concise but descriptive
- Use prefixes: `feature/`, `fix/`, `hotfix/`, `release/`, `chore/`

